{"tid":633623,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)躲藏 特警雄風 甜景太平洋","createTime":"2018-04-18T13:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T18:59:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae351f1fb2da4715fe27b8ee95f334359a14f75","tid":633623,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=vLOIvQpHADFCD3I8K525qaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5956fb02\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=vLOIvQpHADFCD3I8K525qaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cf69b69b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=vLOIvQpHADFCD3I8K525qaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a252ad06\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/qu20884/1456404750-1373048053_n.jpg?v=1456404753\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fqu20884%2F1456404750-1373048053_n.jpg%3Fv%3D1456404753&h=40b14879&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/84/S.W.A.T._Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F84%2FS.W.A.T._Poster.jpg&h=d358b856&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/03/Pacific_Rim_Uprising_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F03%2FPacific_Rim_Uprising_Poster.jpg&h=03b707d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.自從雷、克萊兒和他們的女兒柔伊找到地下避難所已經過301天了。由於完全無法消去他們內心的恐懼，他們一直冀望有天可以回到地面過正常的家庭生活，然而地面上等著他們的，是更深沉的恐懼<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述「反恐特警組」為洛杉磯警察局中最菁英的特警部隊，但在一次銀行搶案的行動使得該部隊被迫改組，而成員之一的吉姆也與隊友甘布爾難翻而拆夥。後來，警局為了挽救形象而請來老鳥哈里遜上尉來組成全新的反恐特警組，使得被轉至槍械室的熱血警官吉姆、單親媽媽與首位女成員克麗絲、風趣的戴克、神槍手T&middot;J與吉姆前妻的哥哥巴斯特全被哈里遜找來受訓，以成為受到長官認同的菁英<br />\n<br />\n3.故事背景設定於突破點之戰的10年後，人類用以戰勝外星巨獸「怪獸」（Kaiju）[註 2]的巨型武裝機器人「機甲獵人」（Jaeger）已成為了人類史上最強大的全球防禦力量。當怪獸的威脅再度降臨時，機甲獵人計畫注入了年輕的新血，以對抗強大的怪獸勢力<br />\n<br />\n9 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=vLOIvQpHADFCD3I8K525qaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=bc87b60e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=vLOIvQpHADFCD3I8K525qaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0abeccb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326ad0b6dddb6588ab612cfeea68deb34038a84d","tid":633623,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chick